## Limitations

The findings are based on available online resources and may not cover all aspects of sales promotion infrastructure globally. The data is limited to the perspectives and insights provided by the sources accessed, which may not fully represent the diversity of conditions in every country. Additionally, the lack of specific data on certain countries may lead to a generalized view rather than a detailed analysis of each region's infrastructure capabilities.